; ブルー再離脱～最終決戦




;■ポラリスの降臨とブルーの最期

;◇イベント01・魔石をそろえてポラリスを呼び出す
*advent_1

; ☆フリーモード
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*advent_1 cond='game.isFreeMode'

; ポラリスの神殿・祭壇
@saveon
@eval exp='game.party.minimumRecovery()
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=01]「We did it! Finally, all 12 crystals are glowing!」[k]
At last we have collected 12 magic stones and brought them to this altar. All the crystals on the altar reacted and began to glow with a divine light.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp057 f=polaris_99]「Everyone, you did a great job!」[k]
Out of nowhere, I hear the voice of Lady Polaris.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp058 f=polaris_99]「You have collected 12 magic stones. Now I can descend to earth.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Lady Polaris...!」[k]
At last, Lady Polaris is coming down to earth. Finally, that demon will be defeated![k]
[ポラリス v=vp059 f=polaris_99]「Now, let us begin the ritual of the descent. Bring the 12 magic stones over here.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Okay. So then...」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm217 f=07]「That's not gonna happen!」[k]
; ↑ 突然、乗り込んでくるムールムール。怒り気味で
[textoff]
@st
@image layer=e0 storage=PE_base_view visible=true mode=psdodge
@image layer=e1 storage=9999 visible=false
@playse storage=bomber
@startemit layer=e0 storage=PE_bombfire time=500
@wait time=300
@anime_fadein layer=e1
@wait time=500
@clearemit layer=e0
@quake time=500 hmax=20 vmax=10
@walk turn=n cond='WAY != "n"'
@walk move=s
[texton]
∗boom!∗[k]
[テオ f=09]「...!」[k]
[マックス f=11]「Wow! What is that?!」[k]
@anime_fadeout layer=e1
The moment we heard that voice, a fireball from behind burst into the altar and exploded![k]
[テオ f=12]「W-what happened?!」[k]
[textoff]
@wait time=500
@walk turn=s
@wait time=500
@mu f=murmur
@fg c=ムールムール f=07
[texton]
[ムールムール v=vm218 f=07]「Idiot! I'll never let that god descend!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Y-you...!」[k]
When I turned around, there was Murmur![k]
@jump target=*_gameover_murmur cond='! game.guest.members.has(o.ブルー)'
Damn... We were followed...![k]
[ムールムール v=vm219 f=07]「I wondered what was going on since you were busy collecting gems, but I didn't realize it was to summon that damn god! If I'd found out a bit later, I'd have been in real trouble!」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Damn it... what a jerk...!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「...Ah!」[k]
I rush to check the altar.[k]
...Thank goodness, the altar is safe. We can still perform the ritual of descent for Lady Polaris.[k]
[テオ f=05]「The ritual will have to wait! Come on everyone, let's stop her first!」[k]
[マックス f=07]「Got it!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm220 f=07]「There's no way I'm gonna let a god come down here! I'll kill you all right here!」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「You're going to kill us, are you?」[k]
Blue steps in front of Murmur with a wry smile on his face.[k]
[ブルー f=01]「You're a fool to come back to be killed again. A demon who doesn't learn.」[k]
@fg c=ムールムール f=06
[ムールムール f=06]「...」[k]
@se f=sword
∗draw∗[k]
[ブルー f=01]「I'll burn you to ashes as many times as I have to. Brace yourself, Miredy!」[k]
Blue draws his saber and confronts Murmur![k]
@fg c=ムールムール f=07
[ムールムール v=vm221 f=07]「That attitude really pisses me off! Okay, I'll kill you first! Breath of Death!」[k]
[textoff]

@image layer=5 storage=screen_deepblackfull
@anime_fadein layer=5
