[texton]
[テオ f=11]「Blue! Please!」[k]
Fatal breath is released from Murmur's mouth! But Blue's demon hunter power should be able to prevent it.[k]
[ブルー f=15]「You idiot! Have you forgotten that your moves don't work on me?」[k]
[textoff]

@se f=shakin4
@image layer=9 storage=9999 visible=true opacity=0
@move layer=9 time=1000 path=,,255
