[texton]
[テオ f=11]「...!」[k]
[ブルー f=11]「What?」[k]
[ムールムール f=14]「... ∗grin∗」[k]
The force of the breath is unstoppable?![k]
Her fatal breath passes through the barrier of light, unable to be blocked by Blue's demon hunter power! That's ridiculous![k]
[ムールムール v=vm223 f=03]「Gahahaha! That won't work anymore!」[k]
; ↑ 優位に立って喜ぶ
[ムールムール v=vm224 f=15]「This breath is more powerful than last time! Now, take a deep breath of death and die!」[k]
[textoff]

