[texton]
[ブルー f=11]「Guaaaaaaah!」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn094 f=11]「Blue!」[k]
; ↑ 叫ぶ
Blue was hit directly by Murmur's fatal breath![k]
[textoff]

@anime_fadeout layer=5,6,7
@layopt layer=5 index=6000
@clearemit layer=7
@wait time=500
@fgf c=ブルー f=10

[texton]
[ブルー f=10]「S-shit...」[k]
[textoff]

@clf
@se f=dosa
@quake time=200 hmax=10 vmax=5
@wait time=700
@eval exp='o.ブルー.setStatus(o.死亡, true)'
@eval exp='o.ブルー.retire()'

[texton]
[サンドラ v=vn095 f=27]「Blue!」[k]
; ↑ 悲鳴
Blue fell to the ground in a crumpled heap. The power of the fatal breath had killed him.[k]
[サンドラ v=vn096 f=29]「Blue! Blue!」[k]
Sandra violently shakes the fallen Blue, and frantically calls out to him. However, Blue does not respond.[k]
[テオ f=09]「Damn...! What the...!」[k]
I can't believe that even with demon hunter powers it couldn't be blocked...! Who would have thought that Murmur's power had increased to that extent...![k]
@fg c=ムールムール f=15
[ムールムール v=vm225 f=15]「You see? This is what I can really do! My fully recovered, full power breath of death can't be stopped!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm226 f=03]「After being hit with all that breath, even a church can't save him now! Gahahahahahaha! It feels great!」[k]
[テオ f=09]「Damn...!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm227 f=15]「Now, I'll make you guys just like Blue!」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Aaaaahhhh! Help meeeeeee!」[k]
Max is in a panic, trying to find a way to escape.[k]
But Murmur stands at the entrance of the room, blocking our way out. There is no escape for us.[k]
[テオ f=09]「Damn... What do I do?!」[k]
This means it's the end for us this time...![k]
[ムールムール v=vm228 f=15]「Breath of Death!」[k]
[textoff]

