@fa
[マックス f=12]「Ahhhh, help meeeeeee... wait, what?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「...?」[k]
The breath... isn't reaching us...?[k]
Shockingly, just as it seemed we were finished, Murmur's fatal breath failed to touch us.[k]
@layopt layer=6 opacity=64
@wait time=50
@clearemit layer=6
@fg c=ムールムール f=27
[ムールムール v=vm229 f=27]「What's going on?! What happened?!」[k]
Murmur is confused. She hastily looks around. Then [―――][k]
[textoff]

@image layer=7 page=back storage=screen_yellowlight visible=true
@trans method=crossfade time=500
@wt
