@mu f=shrine
[texton]
[テオ f=12]「This is...!」[k]
Suddenly, our party was enveloped in a holy white light.[k]
[テオ f=06]「This white light... Could it once again be the power to exorcise demons?」[k]
But I didn't invoke this power, and since Blue is dead, neither did he.[k]
So who on earth did it this time?![k]
[name n=Polaris v=vp060 key=ポラリス buf=12]「Phew, I made it just in time.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「...!」[k]
I heard the voice of Lady Polaris.[k]
But it wasn't a voice that echoed throughout the temple like before. It sounds like a person speaking right here.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Lady Polaris?! Where are you?」[k]
[textoff]

@anime_fadeout layer=7,e2
@layopt layer=7 page=back visible=false
@clearemit layer=e2
@clf
@w05
@walk turn=n
@w05

[texton]
I hurriedly turned back toward the altar.[k]
[textoff]

@fg c=polaris_lighten top=-20
@w05
[texton]
Then I saw a shining figure floating there, glowing with a soft light.[k]
[テオ f=05]「...?」[k]
A silhouette wrapped in light. Its radiance gradually subsides, and gradually a shape becomes visible.[k]
[textoff]

@fg c=ポラリス f=04 t=1000
@w05
[texton]
[？？？]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「A child...?」[k]
It was a young girl. She had white wings on her back and floated in front of me, glowing faintly.[k]
Could it be that this girl is...?![k]
[textoff]

@fg c=ポラリス f=02 t=1000
@w05
[texton]
[ポラリス v=vp061 f=02]「I am Polaris, God of Harmony. I have descended to earth by the power of the magic stones.」[k]
[マックス f=11]「What?!」[k]
[   if exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve091 f=12]「S-seriously...? This girl...?!」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs092 f=12]「S-seriously...? This girl...?!」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg078 f=12]「S-seriously...? This girl...?!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd088 f=12]「S-seriously...? This girl...?!」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM'][リム v=vh090 f=12]「S-seriously...? This girl...?!」[k]
[endif]
[テオ f=12]「You're... Lady Polaris?」[k]
A young girl like this is a god...?! I can't believe it...![k]
[ポラリス v=vp062 f=01]「Are you surprised that I look like a child? But this is how I appear in the human world.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「I-I see...」[k]
What a surprise. Such a lovely girl was the god I had always worshiped.[k]
So, it was you who protected us from the fatal breath just now, Lady Polaris?[k]
[ポラリス v=vp063 f=02]「It was really a close call. I used my holy power to stop the breath of death!」[k]
[テオ f=13]「I see... Thank you for your help.」[k]
I knew it... No matter how powerful a devil's breath is, it's no wonder that a god's power can block it.[k]
@fg c=ポラリス f=07
[ポラリス v=vp064 f=07]「...Well, now we have to defeat Murmur!」[k]
; ↑ 厳しい口調で
Lady Polaris' expression changes and she glares at Murmur.[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@w05
@walk turn=s
@w05
@fgf c=ムールムール f=27
@mu f=murmur
[texton]
[ムールムール v=vm230 f=27]「What is this?! What the hell are you all doing?!」[k]
; ↑ かんしゃくを起こす
@fgf c=ムールムール f=53
[ムールムール v=vm231 f=53]「You're always getting in my way! How much are you gonna interfere before you're satisfied?! Ooooooh, you really piss me off!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp065 f=07]「Now that I am here, I will no longer allow you to do as you please! Now, be quiet and be sealed!」[k]
@fgf c=ムールムール f=08
[ムールムール v=vm232 f=08]「...Tch!」[k]
@se f=wing2
@fg c=8002 left=440 top=-60
Murmur flapped her wings vigorously and quickly flew to the exit.[k]
[テオ f=07]「Wait! You're running away?!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp066 f=07]「Wait! You intend to flee?!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm233 f=07]「Huh?! Why would I stick around for a fight I can't win right now?!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm234 f=07]「But don't get cocky! You're all gonna die once my tower is completed anyway!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm235 f=07]「So enjoy yourselves while you can! Die, idiots!」[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@se f=wing2
@cl
@w05
[texton]
Murmur flew away again, cursing as she went.[k]
Damn... She got away again...![k]
@mu f=shrine
@fg c=ポラリス f=01
[ポラリス v=vp067 f=01]「Are you all right, everyone?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Y-yes... Except Blue.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp068 f=01]「I was surprised by Murmur's sudden attack. I almost couldn't descend.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Speaking of which, how did you descend, Lady Polaris? I thought we needed to complete the ritual.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp069 f=02]「Well... The ritual isn't strictly necessary.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp070 f=02]「All that is needed for my manifestation is the altar and the 12 magic stones. Since the magic stones were all here, all I had to do was wait for my body to materialize.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp071 f=02]「If the altar had been destroyed or the magic stones scattered before my descent was complete, it would have been the end. I am glad that we managed to avoid the worst!」[k]
[テオ f=14]「I see... Anyway, I'm glad you descended safely.」[k]
It was a close call... We can only be thankful for our good fortune.[k]
Anyway, we have finally accomplished the great task of Lady Polaris' descent. Now it's our turn to go on the offensive.[k]
Speaking of which, what happened to Sandra? ...And Blue.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Sandra, is Blue...」[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@w05
@walk turn=e
@w05
[texton]
[ブルー e=通常 f=19]「...」[k]
When I looked, I saw that Blue was still lying still. Nearby, Sandra is wearing a very serious expression on her face.[k]
@fg c=サンドラ f=56
[サンドラ v=vn097 f=56]「...I tried using resurrection powder... But it doesn't seem to be working at all.」[k]
; ↑ 意気消沈。『復活の粉』は回復アイテムの一種
[テオ f=12]「Unbelievable...!」[k]
Resurrection powder won't bring him back to life...?! That's ridiculous...[k]
Blue was hit by a huge concentration of fatal breath. Maybe that's the cause...[k]
Come to think of it, Murmur also said something to the effect that Blue could no longer be saved. Does this mean that too much exposure to the breath of death is truly fatal?[k]
@fg c=サンドラ f=57
[サンドラ v=vn098 f=57]「Hey, God. Can't you save this man?」[k]
Sandra appeals to Lady Polaris with sullen eyes.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp072 f=06]「...I'm sorry, but after being exposed to that much fatal breath, even I, a god...」[k]
@fg c=サンドラ f=10
[サンドラ v=vn099 f=10]「Oh no...」[k]
Sandra's shoulders slump in resignation. She really did care for Blue...[k]
[ポラリス v=vp073 f=51]「...I cannot return the dead to life. Life and death are the domain of Zola, the god of life and death. Only holy magic and human prayer can override that.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp074 f=06]「As you humans always do, place the body in a church and pray for the resurrection with the help of the clergy. That is all I can say.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn100 f=10]「...Understood.」[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w1

