@gameon
@mu f=garden
@fg c=ポラリス f=01
[texton w=1]
[ポラリス v=vp075 f=01]「Now, I shall accompany you all. Let's defeat Murmur together!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yes, thank you very much, Lady Polaris.」[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@st
@se f=up3
@eval exp='game.guest.entry(o.ポラリス)'
@notice text="<y>Polaris has joined the party!"
@mu f=&'game.map.bgm'
[texton w=1]
We've finally come this far...! This time, we're going to settle it with Murmur.[k]
With the addition of Lady Polaris, we are completely free from the fear of fatal breath. From now on, we can go into battle with that devil without hesitation.[k]
@eval exp='game.curChara = game.wife'
[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh091 f=02]「We're finally here, aren't we, my love?」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve092 f=02]「We're finally here, my love.」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd089 f=02]「We're finally here, aren't we, my love?」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg079 f=02]「We're finally here, aren't we, my love?」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs093 f=02]「We're finally here, my love.」[k]
[endif]
[テオ f=02]「Yes.」[k]
Now [ヒロイン] is free from Blue. We can finally be a couple again. I'm honestly happy about it, though I feel a little bad for the fallen Blue.[k]
[マックス f=01]「It's time for the final showdown! Of course, I'll be with you guys until the end!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Thank you, Max.」[k]
[サンドラ f=10]「...」[k]
Sandra remained by Blue's body with her head bowed.[k]
[テオ f=05]「...What will you do now, Sandra?」[k]
@fg c=サンドラ e=戦闘 f=13
[サンドラ v=vn101 f=13]「I shall go to the church to bet on Blue's revival. So I suppose this is goodbye.」[k]
; ↑ 力なく笑う
[テオ f=06]「Is that so... that's unfortunate」[k]
@fg c=サンドラ f=14
[サンドラ v=vn102 f=14]「I really wanted to stay with you until the end, but... I'm sorry.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「No, it's fine. Thank you for everything.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
@se f=period
@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.ブルー)'
@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.サンドラ)'
@notice text="<y>Blue and Sandra left the party."
[texton]
I never thought I would part ways with Blue in this way... I hated him, but things turning out like this is a little sad.[k]
But this is no time for sentimentality. Next time we must defeat Murmur.[k]
This time I'll settle it! Wait and see, demon![k]
[textoff]
