;◇イベント02・ポラリスと会話
*advent_2

; 翌朝の宿屋ロビー
@saveon
@w05
@bg f=0003
@mu f=happy
[texton w=1]
Next morning.[k]
[テオ f=05]「What do you think we should do now, Lady Polaris?」[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=ポラリス f=08
[texton]
[ポラリス v=vp076 f=08]「Head for the tower that Murmur was building. I am sure she will be there.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Understood.」[k]
Thinking about it, she said before she left, that when the tower was complete, we'd all die.[k]
Rumor has it that the tower is steadily getting higher. Maybe we should hurry.[k]
[テオ f=01]「Speaking of which, what did you do last night, Lady Polaris?」[k]
@fg c=ポラリス f=52
[ポラリス v=vp077 f=52]「Eh? Of course, I slept in bed just like everyone else.」[k]
@fg c=ポラリス f=04
[ポラリス v=vp078 f=04]「I, who have come down to earth, am the same as all of you, except for my divine power.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp079 f=04]「I sleep at night, I eat, I even take a bath.」[k]
[テオ f=13]「I-I see...」[k]
@fg c=ポラリス f=01
[ポラリス v=vp080 f=01]「So everyone, please treat me as one of your own!」[k]
[テオ f=13]「Y-yes.」[k]
@fg c=ポラリス f=03
[ポラリス v=vp081 f=03]「Actually, I am really looking forward to my first adventure with humans in a long time!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp082 f=03]「I am very excited. Let's have fun together, everyone!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Y-yes...」[k]
Lady Polaris seems to be very excited. Is it like a field trip?[k]
Well, it's great that she's motivated. Lady Polaris' power is essential for the final battle, so let's join forces and truly defeat the devil this time.[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w05
[hoteloff]




;■ラドミラの塔

;◇イベント01・ラドミラの塔へ
*radmila_1

; 大峡谷入口
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*radmila_1 cond='game.isFreeMode'
@wait time=500 cond='WAY != "w"'
@walk turn=w cond='WAY != "w"'
@wait time=500
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「That's...!」[k]
In the distance, a tower of tremendous height dominates the skyline.[k]
That must be the tower Mr. Schwartz was talking about. When did it get so high...?![k]
[ポラリス v=vp083 f=08]「That is the Radmira Tower that Murmur was trying to build. She must be in there.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Murmur is there...」[k]
Murmur tricked or coerced many humans into building this tower.[k]
But what on earth does that devil intend to do by building such a huge tower?[k]
[ポラリス v=vp084 f=08]「I don't know what her purpose is, but being her, I am sure she is going to do something!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp085 f=07]「You are our only hope! Please stop Murmur's schemes!」[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇イベント02・塔の入口を開く
*radmila_2

; 塔の入口前
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*radmila_2 cond='game.isFreeMode'
@wait time=500
[texton]
We reach a tower, but its entrance is closed by a solid stone door.[k]
Its stone door is very sturdy and doesn't so much as budge when pushed hard.[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff cond='! game.guest.members.has(o.ポラリス)']
@fg c=ポラリス f=01
[texton]
[ポラリス v=vp086 f=01]「With my power, a door of this size is nothing to worry about.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp087 f=02]「Please step back a little.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
@wait time=500
@walk move=e
@wait time=500
@fg c=7001 left=600 top=100
@wait time=500
@playse storage=tremble
@quake time=3000 hmax=5 vmax=0
*rrrrumble*[auto time=1000]
@stopquake
@playse storage=rockdrop
@changewall x=1 y=4 way=w himg=arch type=space behind=true
@changefloor x=1 y=4 warp=b
@wait time=500
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「Ah...!」[k]
When Lady Polaris held out her hand, that heavy looking door was easily opened.[k]
[テオ f=01]「Thank you, Lady Polaris.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
@fg c=ポラリス f=07
[texton]
[ポラリス v=vp088 f=07]「Now, let's climb this tower! Together, we will stop that devil's scheme!」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Yes, Lady Polaris!」[k]
@cl
...Though having said that, how will we attack this huge tower?[k]
From the looks of it, there are 20 or more floors. Climbing a tower of this magnitude will probably require some very careful preparation.[k]
We could continue into the tower, but it might be better to go back to town and prepare first.[k]
[textoff]
@delevent
[eventoff]


;◇イベント03・女湯にワープさせられる
*radmila_3
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*radmila_3 cond='game.isFreeMode'
@warp map=温泉・浴場 x=9 y=17 way=w
@eval exp='game.map.changeObject(%[pimg: "mob07"], 9, 16, "f")'
@eval exp='game.updateView()'
@wait time=2000
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「...Hmm? Is this...?」[k]
I've been somewhere like this before... A hot spring?![k]
[textoff]
@walk turn=s
@cl t=1000
[texton]
[name n="Female Bather" f=priest_white_03]「Kyaaa!」[k]
[name n="Female Bather" f=archer_purple_03]「Hey! Why is there a man here?!」[k]
[テオ f=37]「What...?!」[k]
Oh no! It looks like we've warped into the women's bath![k]
[マックス f=21]「Oh, wow! This is a spectacular sight!」[k]
[name n="Female Bather" f=bladesman_red_03]「Don't look at me! Get the hell out of here!」[k]
[テオ f=37]「I-I'm so sorry!」[k]
[textoff]
@walk move=n
@walk move=e
@walk move=e
@walk move=e
@walk move=e
@walk move=e
@black on
@wait time=500
[texton]
We escaped from the women's bath in a panic![r]
We were exploring the tower then got sent to a crazy place...[k]
[name f=other_03]Damn you, Murmur. I can't believe you pulled this prank on us...![k]
[textoff]
@wait time=500
@warp map=ヤネクの森・東 x=6 y=29 way=n sound=door1
@black off
[eventoff]


;◇イベント04・サンダードラゴンと戦闘
*radmila_4

; 途中階
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*radmila_4 cond='game.isFreeMode'
@saveon
@mu f=murmur
[texton]
[ムールムール v=vm236 f=07]「Hey! You guys!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...!」[k]
Suddenly, I heard Murmur's voice from behind me![k]
[textoff]
@wait time=800
@walk turn=e
@walk turn=n
@walk move=n
@walk move=w
@walk move=w
@wait time=800
@fg c=8005 left=450 top=60
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=05]「Murmur...!」[k]
Halfway up the tower, Murmur made a surprise appearance.[k]
Murmur is in the middle of the room, wielding her spear and glaring at us hatefully.[k]
[ムールムール v=vm237 f=07]「You guys are really persistent! Why are you following me?」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp089 f=07]「To stop your plans, Murmur!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm238 f=08]「Polaris...! You came here too...」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp090 f=07]「Murmur, why are you building such a tower? Stop harming humans!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm239 f=07]「You're so annoying! Don't try and order me around!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm240 f=07]「This tower was built so that anyone could get to the heavenly realm where the gods live!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp091 f=07]「To heaven...? What are you going to do once you get there?!」[k]
@fg c=satan left=450 top=60
[ムールムール v=vm241 f=15]「Isn't it obvious? I'm going to take revenge on those annoying gods!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm242 f=15]「Inciting the the demons of the underworld to climb this tower and invade the heavens would cause chaos there! And the earth where humans live might be destroyed too!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp092 f=11]「W-why would you do that...?!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm243 f=15]「I told you! Revenge! This is punishment for all the suffering you've caused us! You deserve it!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Damn you... devil...!」[k]
We must stop her evil schemes at all costs. We must protect the earth... and humanity.[k]
[ムールムール v=vm244 f=07]「I won't let anyone interfere with my plans! You're all going to die here! Come out, Thunder Dragon!」[k]
@se f=roar
@fg l=9011 left=220 top=0
[name n="Thunder Dragon" f=dragon_02]「Roaaaaar!」[k]
A huge dragon appeared before us![k]
@fg c=satan left=450 top=60
[ムールムール v=vm245 f=04]「Well then, I'll leave the rest to you!」[k]
@cl c
[ポラリス v=vp093 f=08]「Stop! Murmur!」[k]
[テオ f=11]「Wait! Murmur!」[k]
[textoff]
@cl l b
@se f=roar
@fg c=9012 left=450 top=0
[texton]
[name n="Thunder Dragon" f=dragon_02]「Roaaaaar!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Damn...!」[k]
When I tried to chase after the fleeing Murmur, the dragon she had summoned blocked the way.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp094 f=08]「There's no other choice. Let's defeat this dragon first!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「I understand!」[k]
[textoff]
@clf

; サンダードラゴンと戦闘
@monster pos=3 name=サンダードラゴン
@callbattle bgm=dragon gameover=true escape=false
@notice text="Defeated the Thunder Dragon!"
@delevent

@eval exp='dm("シナリオ  ")'
[texton w=0]
Somehow, we managed to defeat the dragon. However, Murmur escaped somewhere.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp095 f=07]「Let's hurry and chase after Murmur! We must stop her plans!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Yes, Lady Polaris!」[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff bgm]


;◇イベント05・ムールムールと最終決戦
*radmila_5

; 最上階
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*radmila_5 cond='game.isFreeMode'
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「There she is...!」[k]
We discovered Murmur standing alone on what finally appears to be the roof![k]
[textoff]
@fg c=8006 left=450 top=60
[texton w=1]
[ムールムール v=vm246 f=11]「What? You've already got this far?」[k]
@fg c=8004 left=450 top=60
[ムールムール v=vm247 f=53]「Ugh! You're so annoying! Annoying, annoying, annoying! When are you gonna give up chasing me?!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp096 f=07]「Murmur! Give up! There's nowhere left for you to run!」[k]
@fg c=8005 left=450 top=60
[ムールムール v=vm248 f=07]「What? What are you getting so cocky about? There's no way the great Murmur would lose to the likes of you!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm249 f=07]「Since it comes to this, I'll crush you guys with all my might! I'll make you regret coming this far!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...!」[k]
The devil raised her spear high and yelled skywards.[k]
[ムールムール v=vm250 f=07]「Come! Greater Demons!」[k]
@fg l=demon_black left=230 top=-40 b
@fg c=8005 left=450 top=60 b
@fg r=demon_black left=630 top=-40
Then, two Greater Demons appeared on either side of her![k]
[ムールムール v=vm251 f=07]「Let's settle this!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Here it comes! Everyone, get ready!」[k]
This time, I'll defeat this devil! I will put an end to this dreadful battle![k]
[textoff]
@clf

