[ムールムール v=vm253 f=28]「You gotta be kidding... I can't lose here! Not until I unleash my true demonic power to take revenge on the heavenly realm...」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm254 f=28]「...If I lose here, I'll lose everything... So there's no choice but to use it now! My true power!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What...?!」[k]
@fg c=8007 left=450 top=60
[ムールムール v=vm255 f=17]「Ooooooooooooooooooooo!」[k]
