Then, a vortex of evil energy converged on Murmur and she began to release enormous magical power![k]
[ポラリス v=vp097 f=11]「No! Don't let her use that power!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What do you mean, Lady Polaris?!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp098 f=11]「Murmur is unleashing her hidden magical powers to awaken her true demonic abilities! Once that happens, there's no stopping her!」[k]
[テオ f=11]「What?! Then we have to stop it quickly!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm256 f=15]「You idiot! It's too late!」[k]
[textoff]

