[魔公ムールムール v=vm257 f=03]「Hahahahaha! Now you guys will never be able to beat me! Serves you right!」[k]
[魔公ムールムール v=vm258 f=01]「In this form, I can ascend to the heavens! I'll take revenge on the gods and rule over both gods and mortals from the heavens! Hahahaha!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp100 f=08]「Damn...!」[k]
[魔公ムールムール v=vm259 f=02]「...But first, I have to deal with you annoying people.」[k]
[魔公ムールムール v=vm260 f=15]「I'm going to kill all of you right now! Be prepared!」[k]
