[texton w=1]
[テオ f=01]「Thank you very much for your help, Lady Polaris.」[k]
@fg c=ポラリス f=02
[ポラリス v=vp110 f=02]「No, thank you all for defeating the devil. Without you, the world would have been in big trouble.」[k]
@fg c=ポラリス f=03
[ポラリス v=vp111 f=03]「All of you here are undoubtedly true heroes. I would like to express my heartfelt admiration for your courage.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Thank you very much, I am honored.」[k]
[マックス f=03]「Oh my, God praised me! I'm so embarrassed!」[k]
@fg c=ポラリス f=02
[ポラリス v=vp112 f=02]「Well then, I will return to the heavenly realm. If anything else happens, please come to my temple.」[k]
