[texton w=1]
With those words, Lady Polaris ascended to the heavens in a pillar of light.[k]
[テオ f=05]「...」[k]
@eval exp='game.curChara = game.wife'
@fg c=キャラ f=02

[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh094 f=04]「It's finally over, isn't it?」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve095 f=02]「It's finally over, isn't it?」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd092 f=03]「It's finally over, isn't it?」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg082 f=02]「It's finally over, isn't it?」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs096 f=01]「It's finally over, isn't it?」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=02]「Yes, it's finally over.」[k]
My smiling wife... Yes, the greatest reward from this adventure is my beloved wife.[k]
I will continue to be an adventurer. And I will always be with my precious companion.[k]
@fg c=キャラ f=22

[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh095 f=22]「So, that... Actually, I have something to report to you.」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve096 f=22]「So, that... Actually, I have something to tell you.」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd093 f=22]「So, that... Actually, I have something to report to you.」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg083 f=22]「So, that... Actually, I have something to report to you...」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs097 f=22]「So, that... Actually, I have something to tell you.」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=05]「Is something wrong?」[k]
@fg c=キャラ f=24

[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh096 f=24]「Just now, Lady Polaris secretly told me as she was leaving... that there is a new life growing inside me...」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve097 f=24]「Just now, Lady Polaris secretly told me as she was leaving... that there is a new life growing inside me...」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd094 f=24]「Just now, Lady Polaris secretly told me as she was leaving... She said there's a new life growing inside me...」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg084 f=24]「Just now, Lady Polaris secretly told me as she was leaving... that there is a new life growing inside me...」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs098 f=24]「Just now, Lady Polaris secretly told me as she was leaving... that there is a new life growing inside me...」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=05]「Which means...!」[k]
[ヒロイン f=22]「... ∗nod∗」[k]
[ヒロイン] nodded with a smile. Her eyes were filled with joy.[k]
@clf
@se f=dosa
@quake time=500 hmax=10 vmax=10
[テオ f=01]「[ヒロイン]...」[k]
Overcome with emotion, I hugged my wife tightly.[k]
I love my wife so much...! I will continue to love this woman forever...![k]
I've been through a lot of tough times. But I've overcome them all, and now I'm going to be happy with this woman.[k]
Feeling her body heat, I was thrilled by the anticipation of the happiness that was to come.[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out t=2000
@wait time=1500




;■エンディング

[texton w=0]
A few months later.[k]
I took my pregnant wife with me and returned to my parents' house for the first time in ages.[k]
When I introduced my wife to my mother, and told her about the baby in [ヒロイン]'s womb, she was overjoyed.[k]
I became a full-fledged adventurer and would produce a successor. I was relieved to be able to give good news.[k]

; セックス回数等によりバッドエンディングへ
@jump target=*bad_ending cond='game.date < f.lastBlueSexDay + 60 && game.wife.sexCount.blue > game.wife.sexCount.theo'

After that, my wife gave birth safely, and a new life began for the three of us: me, my wife, and our child.[k]
[textoff]
@w1

; 主人公の子を出産エンド → 各ヒロインシナリオへ
@jump storage="heroine01b.scn" target=*good_ending cond='isHUM'
@jump storage="heroine02b.scn" target=*good_ending cond='isELF'
@jump storage="heroine03b.scn" target=*good_ending cond='isDWA'
@jump storage="heroine04b.scn" target=*good_ending cond='isGNO'
@jump storage="heroine05b.scn" target=*good_ending cond='isSYL'


;◇バッドエンディング・ブルーの子を出産エンド
*bad_ending
After that, my wife gave birth safely, and our child grew up healthy and strong, and everything went smoothly.[k]
[textoff]
@w1
[texton w=0]
...Or so I thought.[k]
[textoff]
@w1

@bg f=0007 cond='isHUM || isDWA || isSYL'
@bg f=0060 cond='isGNO'
@bg f=0048 cond='isELF'
@mu f=evil
[texton w=1]
Three years later.[k]
[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh097 e=通常 f=01]「Hey, don't be naughty, Aoki!」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve098 e=通常 f=64]「Hey, don't be so naughty, Aoki.」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd095 e=通常 f=03]「Hey, don't be naughty～, Aoki～!」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg085 e=通常 f=05]「Hey, don't be naughty, Aoki.」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs099 e=通常 f=62]「Hey! Aoki! Eat your dinner properly!」[k]
[endif]

[テオ e=通常 f=06]「...」[k]
It has been more than three years since I got married to my wife. Our child is growing up healthily, and the three of us are building a happy family.[k]
However... there is something that really bothers me.[k]

[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh098 f=17]「Hey, Aoki! Listen to mommy!」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve099 f=07]「Hey, Aoki! Stop being so stubborn and listen to your mother!」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd096 f=54]「Aoki～! Please listen to mom～!」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg086 f=09]「Hey, please, Aoki... I want you to listen to your mother...」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs100 f=17]「Come on, Aoki, listen to your mother!」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Aoki is my son's name. He is so mischievous that he doesn't seem like my son, and even at the age of three, he already shows a strength of mind and shrewdness that is uncharacteristic of a child.[k]
And... occasionally, he gives me, his father, a sharp look that makes me feel uneasy as a parent.[k]
[name n=Azure]「... ∗stare∗」[k]
[テオ f=12]「...! ∗gulp∗」[k]
Those eyes... they held a frightening look that seemed somehow familiar.[k]
For some reason, I can't shake off this uneasy feeling about my child.[k]
Suddenly, a terrifying thought crossed my mind. I desperately tried to shake it off, telling myself over and over again that I must not destroy this happiness.[k]
[textoff]
