*_gameover_murmur
Didn't she die...?![k]
[ムールムール v=vm219 f=07]「I wondered what was going on since you were busy collecting gems, but I didn't realize it was to summon that damn god! If I'd found out a bit later, I'd have been in real trouble!」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Damn it... what a jerk...!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm220 f=07]「There's no way I'm gonna let a god come down here! I'll kill you all right here!」[k]
[テオ f=09]「...Damn!」[k]
What on earth... I can't believe Murmur is still alive...![k]
What amazing regenerative abilities. This is what a great demon is like. It's beyond the comprehension of us humans.[k]
But what will we do?! I no longer have the power to exorcise demons. Blue, who does, is no longer with us. If things continue like this, we'll...![k]
[ムールムール v=vm228 f=15]「Breath of Death!」[k]
[textoff]

@image layer=5 storage=screen_deepblackfull
@anime_fadein layer=5
@playse storage=howling
@image layer=6 storage=PE_base_full visible=true
@layopt layer=6 top=0 left=0
@startemit layer=6 storage=PE_smoke_red2 time=-1
@wait time=1000

[texton]
[テオ f=12]「...!」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Aaaaahhhh! Help meeeeeee!」[k]
Murmur unleashed her fatal breath![k]
[textoff]

@anime_fadeout layer=5,6
@clearemit layer=6
@fa
@out t=2000
@wait time=1000

[texton]
However, with Blue gone, we had no way to defend against this attack...[k]
[textoff]
@w1
@jump storage="script.ks" target=*_event_game_over
; ゲームオーバー
